raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "4.0.2" %}

package:
  name: django
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/D/Django/Django-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 110fb58fb12eca59e072ad59fc42d771cd642dd7a2f2416582aa9da7a8ef954a

build:
  number: 0
  skip: true  # [py<38]
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  entry_points:
    - django-admin = django.core.management:execute_from_command_line

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - asgiref >=3.4.1,<4
    - backports.zoneinfo  # [py<39]
    - sqlparse >=0.2.2
    - python-tzdata  # [win]

test:
  requires:
    - pip
    # Test optional dependency.
    - psycopg2  # [not win]
  imports:

    - django.apps
